longBusinessSummary: Guangzhou R&F Properties Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the development and sale of residential and commercial properties in the People's Republic of China, Malaysia, Cambodia, Korea, the United Kingdom, and Australia. The company invests in and develops various properties, including hotels, office buildings, shopping malls, logistic parks, and other retail properties in Beijing, Guangzhou, and other cities. It is also involved in the operation and management of hotels; provides property management and leasing, and architectural and engineering design services, as well as marketing development services; and operates a construction company and football club. Guangzhou R&F Properties Co., Ltd. was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China.
address2: 45-54th Floor 10 Huaxia Road Pearl River New Town
